sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 👤 User
    participant Orch as 🎯 Orchestrator<br/>(GEMINI.md)
    participant Agent as 🤖 Specialized<br/>Agent
    participant Log as 📋 CAREER_LOG.md

    User->>Orch: "I need help with..."
    
    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
    Note over Orch: 1. LISTEN & ANALYZE
    Orch->>Orch: Identify user's current phase<br/>Determine which agent needed
    end
    
    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
    Note over Orch,Agent: 2. DELEGATE TO AGENT
    Orch->>Agent: @agent-name: [Task with context]
    Agent->>Agent: Execute specialized work<br/>(deep analysis)
    Agent-->>Orch: Detailed output<br/>(500+ words)
    end
    
    rect rgb(255, 248, 225)
    Note over Orch: 3. SYNTHESIZE & SUMMARIZE
    Orch->>Orch: Extract 2-3 key insights<br/>Discard transcript
    end
    
    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
    Note over Orch,Log: 4. STORE IMPORTANT DATA
    Orch->>Log: Save findings to persistent file<br/>• Opportunities identified<br/>• Gaps analyzed<br/>• Progress made<br/>• Next actions
    end
    
    rect rgb(230, 242, 241)
    Note over Orch,User: 5. COMMUNICATE & GUIDE
    Orch-->>User: 2-3 key bullets<br/>+ "What's next?"
    end
    
    User->>Orch: "What did we do last time?"
    Orch->>Log: Read relevant section
    Log-->>Orch: Previous findings
    Orch-->>User: "Last session we...<br/>Now let's..."

    style User fill:#e1f5ff
    style Orch fill:#fff3e0
    style Agent fill:#f3e5f5
    style Log fill:#e8f5e9